creator: OXIO Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Chipper is a new kind of mobile connectivity provider.


We offer you the best options and you're free to choose the one that suits you best at the best price.

Mi Marca allows you to buy packages of data, minutes and messages over the best network since our Smart Chip is always connecting to the network with the best signal to keep you well connected.

You can buy your packages directly from the app and pay for them with a card or in convenience stores. You can also go to the recharging points to directly buy your packages.
descriptionShort: Control your wireless data: save, buy and browse when you want.
